Phoebe Brand https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Phoebe_Brand 0 Phoebe Brand (November 27, 1907 – July 3, 2004) was an American actress. Brand was born in Syracuse, New York in 1907 and raised in Ilion, Herkimer County, New York. Her father worked for Remington Typewriter Company as a mechanical engineer.
